      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 123
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "说到此处，再也忍耐不住，纵声叫道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 123
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "奔向裘千尺身前，扑入她怀中。她说",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 123
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "纵声笑道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 149
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "举右臂去挡！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 149
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "表妹，你怎地⋯⋯",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 149
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这公孙老儿不知你武功如此了得。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 171
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可是你怎知⋯⋯",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 171
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "杨过心想公孙止利剑不能伤她，其胆已寒，可不能让他知悉其中原委，向公孙止道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 171
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未判定",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "说着抖动黑剑，发出嗡嗡之声。郭芙暗想：",
